  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2026-04-30",
    "date": "2026-05-07T14:29:26Z",
    "text": "This resolution calls on elected officials, faith leaders, and civil society leaders to condemn and counter acts of anti-Semitism.\n\nThe resolution also honors the contributions of Jewish-American\u00a0servicemembers and\u00a0commits to ensuring all Americans, including Jewish Americans, can worship without fear of violence or persecution."
